- Apps provide personalized fitness or football training guidance
- Not a medical service; consult a doctor before starting any program
- Training results may vary by individual

4. Subscription:
- Premium features are accessible via subscription
- Payments processed via official app stores
- Subscription fees are non-refundable unless required by law
- Premium enhances program personalization and guidance

5. Prohibited Conduct:
- No unauthorized access, data scraping, or sharing premium content illegally
- No misuse of the app to harm systems or users

6. Disclaimers:
- Apps are not liable for injuries or health issues
- Programs are suggestions; users follow at their own risk
- Use guidance responsibly

7. Privacy & Data Protection:
- GDPR and KVKK rules apply
- Personal data collected as described in Privacy Policy

8. Modification:
- Terms of Use may be updated; continued use indicates acceptance
- Users will be notified in-app of major changes

9. Governing Law:
- Turkish law applies for users in Turkey
- EU GDPR applies to EU residents
